{"tid":2073993,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【致各黃店一句簡單的說話】","createTime":"2020-06-21T18:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T17:03:25.000Z","uid":23094,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"641d00b897731d05264a6d0347bd5bf351b3333d","tid":2073993,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:26:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">同路人改變消費習慣將資源投放喺你哋身上<br />\n請你哋都改變營運模式嚟回應同路人嘅期望</span></span><br />\n<br />\n表態、參與罷市、支援抗爭、擺放文宣喺舖面...<br />\n呢啲只係成為黃店嘅原因<br />\n但係其實做咗黃店之後有更多嘢可以做<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n選用其他食材/貨品供應商、産地來源<br />\n增設/取消某種付款方式<br />\n播放比較中立嘅電視台/良心歌手嘅歌<br />\n...等等<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈終極目標就係我哋自己養得起自己<br />\n唔使靠支那，要所有紅色、藍色資本捽腳趾玩手指<br />\n除咗係鼓勵更多黃店表態之外<br />\n仲要逼嗰啲冇原則嘅藍店變黃嚟求存<br />\n提升抗爭本錢<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講<br />\n任何業務上嘅決策，都應該將黃色經濟圈納入考慮因素<br />\n<br />\n我唔係針對任何一間黃店<br />\n而係任何一間黃店都應該咁做<br />\n如果黃色經濟圈能夠帶畀你一啲好處<br />\n請你哋做返啲嘢去回應"},{"pid":"dbd1ea975902401d7b85e537af09752cc1997f30","tid":2073993,"uid":30146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8146040e5c4676fd50944ce643f93362e471955","tid":2073993,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:32:56.000Z","msg":"希望各黃店花一分鐘睇呢個Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7045d6e95985e7a3156c9b6273eb84b2a0f620","tid":2073993,"uid":163167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:36:30.000Z","msg":"記住呢啲唔係鬥黃 而係大家都要進步<br />\n繼續支持黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83ecbdb3665a7a3450c6ab9eba50e1e495a068c","tid":2073993,"uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd7045d6e95985e7a3156c9b6273eb84b2a0f620","tid":2073993,"uid":163167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:36:30.000Z","msg":"記住呢啲唔係鬥黃 而係大家都要進步<br />\n繼續支持黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:40:09.000Z","msg":"正想補充<br />\n希望大家唔好用呢樣嘢嚟作為黃店鬥黃嘅指標<br />\n一間舖一間公司做決策時要考慮嘅嘢只有當事人最清楚<br />\n並唔代表佢冇進一步回應同路人嘅期望就代表佢唔夠黃<br />\n我只係鼓勵黃店Keep住行多一步，做多少少"},{"pid":"3ae7b060fdd4922a5c72a90289bd5e56223ee89d","tid":2073993,"uid":23189,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"仲有要做員工陪訓阿<br />\n唔係黃店就可以閪格<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff08241cd43274eb5a3a3980f08231c0ad258c7","tid":2073993,"uid":163167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"各位黃店老闆<br />\n你地嘅影響力絕對比你想像中大<br />\n千祈唔好吝嗇你地嘅力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b191978f10637a60c871ce5db3313ed4dfb39dee","tid":2073993,"uid":23094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ae7b060fdd4922a5c72a90289bd5e56223ee89d","tid":2073993,"uid":23189,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"仲有要做員工陪訓阿<br />\n唔係黃店就可以閪格<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"唔排除有啲黃店已經請緊手足做嘢<br />\n但係可能仲細，啱啱出嚟做嘢<br />\n可能廚藝麻麻，待客未係咁好等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94da8658e291c10bc5e0c2a0dd94f9aa2bf8e228","tid":2073993,"uid":163167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T18:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b019ed13b5fe6e13f58863d5aa50aa2e41c33ed","tid":